      "span_text": "The chemical composition, average grain size, and β-phase content of the as-received alloys are presented in Table 1. * H, O, and N contents were determined by inert gas fusion and the C content by combustion ** The β phase content was determined following a procedure adopted from Tiley et al. by overlaying a regular grid of points on the SEM images and dividing the number of points within the β phase by the total number of points."
